00:51:49.240 --> 00:51:52.880
The ability to read is the most
important tool you'll ever have

00:51:52.880 --> 00:51:56.650
in your life, because it
allows you to unleash this.

00:51:56.650 --> 00:52:00.620
You know, the verbs to read
and to think are synonymous.

00:52:00.620 --> 00:52:02.690
You can't do one without the other.

00:52:02.690 --> 00:52:04.230
It's almost impossible.

00:52:04.230 --> 00:52:06.880
And today, you see a
very divided country.

00:52:06.880 --> 00:52:08.530
I went to UVA Law School.

00:52:08.530 --> 00:52:10.250
I lived in Charlottesville
for 3 years.

00:52:10.250 --> 00:52:11.730
I saw what happened there.

00:52:11.730 --> 00:52:13.970
I saw some of the responses
of people

00:52:13.970 --> 00:52:17.380
that should know better
of what happened there.

00:52:17.380 --> 00:52:21.210
Ignorance and intolerance are
like parentheses or comas,

00:52:21.210 --> 00:52:22.650
you always find them together.

00:52:22.650 --> 00:52:24.340
You never find one
without the other.

00:52:24.340 --> 00:52:27.800
The only way to defeat
ignorance is through education

00:52:27.800 --> 00:52:31.830
and reading is the mainstay
of education, and you get rid

00:52:31.830 --> 00:52:33.740
of ignorance than tolerance
will fall by the wayside.

00:52:33.740 --> 00:52:35.720
If you don't, it never will.

00:52:35.720 --> 00:52:38.190
So, for us, literacy is
the most important tool

00:52:38.190 --> 00:52:41.000
and we have funded programs
virtually in all 50 states

00:52:41.000 --> 00:52:44.500
and counting, millions of dollars
to the Wish You Well Foundation.

00:52:44.500 --> 00:52:47.030 position:56%
We also have a book collection
program called Feeding Body and Mind

00:52:47.030 --> 00:52:51.150
when I do local book events;
we send these big boxes.

00:52:51.150 --> 00:52:53.600
We partnered with Feeding
America which is all

00:52:53.600 --> 00:52:55.160
of the nation's foodbanks.

00:52:55.160 --> 00:52:58.510
