00:53:09.600 --> 00:53:11.890
Illiteracy and poverty
go hand-in-hand.

00:53:11.890 --> 00:53:13.890
It's also most like parentheses;

00:53:13.890 --> 00:53:16.850
most people seeking food
systems have low literacy skills,

00:53:16.850 --> 00:53:20.820
low job skills, that's why
they are not self-sustaining.

00:53:20.820 --> 00:53:22.470
Breaking them out of
that cycle of poverty,

00:53:22.470 --> 00:53:25.160
putting books in their hands
and the hands of their kids,

00:53:25.160 --> 00:53:27.840
I have never seen a bad result
from a book being at home.

00:53:27.840 --> 00:53:32.810
